Feb 13
CATalyst Purrfit Sniper fires a single market order (long or short) at a user-defined date, hour, minute and second, then manages the position with a take-profit target measured in ticks.😼 There is no built-in stop loss 😸.

Important: Must be used on a 1-second chart for accurate timing. On higher timeframes the entry may be delayed by up to one full bar 🙀.

Designed for scheduled news events (CPI, NFP, FOMC, etc.) where you want precise, timed execution 😻.
Feb 13
Release Notes
Added stop loss.
